<refentry id="bif.Reveal" xreflabel="Reveal">

<refmeta>
<indexterm>
<primary>Reveal</primary>
</indexterm>

<refentrytitle>Reveal</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>Reveal</refname>
<refpurpose>
Reveals the actions at an information set to specified players
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
Reveal[infoset->INFOSET, who->LIST(EFPLAYER)] =: INFOSET 
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>Reveal</function> 
reveals the list of actions at <parameter>infoset</parameter> to the players
in <parameter>who</parameter>,
refining their information partitions at
all information sets in the extensive form game accordingly.  
</para>
</refsect1>

</refentry>


